post_text:
In light of COVID-19, we've had to cancel our annual Spring Reception. We were really looking forward to celebrating our school, our amazing scholars, our dedicated staff, our generous supporters, our wonderful community, and our many achievements and successes.
Like everyone else, Equality is reeling from continuing news of racial violence in America. We were founded on the belief that we can achieve Equality. Not by luck, not by chance, but by hard work, and with each of us supporting each other.
Although 2019-2020 has challenged us, this year was extra special for us as well, and points toward a better future.
We are really proud, and very excited, to let you know that we received a 5-year charter renewal and approval to launch our much anticipated expansion to elementary!
Until we can be together again in person, please enjoy this video:
https://charity.gofundme.com/o/en/campaign/socially-distantemotionally-connected

post_text: It was an exciting week up in Albany as the Board of Regents, led by Dr. Betty Rosa, voted to give Equality a 5 year renewal AND expansion to elementary school! To say we are ecstatic and proud is an understatement. We look forward celebrating over the next few months and thank everyone for their continued support!
text: It was an exciting week up in Albany as the Board of Regents, led by Dr. Betty Rosa, voted to give Equality a 5 year renewal AND expansion to elementary school! To say we are ecstatic and proud is an understatement. We look forward celebrating over the next few months and thank everyone for their continued support!

post_text:
In an effort to fundraise for our upcoming competition, the Spring Extravaganza at Six Flags, the dance team has been selling a variety of items through CherryDale. CherryDale had extended our time! We all week to continue to raise funds! Any purchase can be made through myself or any of the dancers. You can also shop at the website at https://www.shopfund.com/Shop , enter the code LHF6743 and SHOP AWAY!! The items you purchase can be sent to the school or to your homes directly! if you have any questions please don't hesitate to ask!

Our GoFundMe is also still up and running! We thoroughly appreciate any donation you are willing to give us. Please share with both your professional and personal networks! We can use all the support we can get!!

post_text: Thank you to the parents who came out for today's high school parent focus group with Ms. Franco, Ms. Norford, and Ms. Benway. We hope to see you all soon!
